title: I was a Teenage Werebear
description: A spoof of 1960's Drive-In flicks, 'I Was a Teenage Werebear' features five rock and roll musical numbers in a mash-up of Roger Corman and John Waters that follows a day in the life of closeted new kid Ricky O'Reilly (played by Sean Paul Lockhart, aka adult film superstar Brent Corrigan) who falls for Malibu High's mysterious bad boy Talon (Anton Troy). When aroused, the two transform into bestial leather daddies, the titular 'werebears'. Written by Anonymous
